Meetings








                            Reporting Safety Concerns
                    








            Reporting Safety Concerns
          


If you do not have the need to remain anonymous, please contact EHSO directly at labsafety@uic.edu. It is much easier to resolve safety issues when EHSO has access to your contact information.
If it is important for you to remain anonymous, please include as much information as possible and report anonymously using the link below.




      Anonymous Safety Concern Report Form
    














